OL,3,CSocial media addiction trial: What
OL,4,Cdoes the landmark US ruling mean for
OL,5,Cthe UK?
OL,7,FWords by ITV News Producer Lois Smith
OL,9,FA US jury on Wednesday found Meta and
OL,10,FYouTube must pay millions of dollars
OL,11,Fin damages, following a landmark trial
OL,12,Fthat accused the tech giants of
OL,13,Fintentionally addicting a young woman
OL,14,Fand injuring her mental health.
OL,16,FThe woman, called Kaley, and her
OL,17,Fmother sued the social media platforms
OL,18,Fover her childhood addiction to social
OL,19,Fmedia, and the subsequent effect that
OL,20,Fhad on her mental health.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774598701
OL,3,CSocial media addiction trial: What
OL,4,Cdoes the landmark US ruling mean for
OL,5,Cthe UK?
OL,7,FThe jury found that the companies
OL,8,Fdesigned their platforms to hook young
OL,9,Fusers, without concern for their well-
OL,10,Fbeing.
OL,12,FMeta, which owns Facebook, Instagram
OL,13,Fand Whatsapp, and Google, which owns
OL,14,FYouTube, were negligent in the design
OL,15,Fof their platforms; knew their design
OL,16,Fwas dangerous; failed to warn of those
OL,17,Frisks; and caused substantial harm to
OL,18,Fthe plaintiff, jurors found.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
