OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774598701
OL,3,CSocial media addiction trial: What
OL,4,Cdoes the landmark US ruling mean for
OL,5,Cthe UK?
OL,7,FThis case in the US is the first of
OL,8,Fits kind to go to trial, and could
OL,9,Finfluence the outcome of thousands of
OL,10,Fsimilar lawsuits accusing social media
OL,11,Fcompanies of deliberately causing harm.
OL,13,FSo how significant is this case, and
OL,14,Fis it likely to impact people in the
OL,15,FUK?
OL,17,FITV News explains.
OL,19,FWhich social media platforms were
OL,20,Fbeing sued and why?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774598701
OL,3,CSocial media addiction trial: What
OL,4,Cdoes the landmark US ruling mean for
OL,5,Cthe UK?
OL,7,FKaley and her mother sued Meta, which
OL,8,Fowns Facebook, Instagram and WhatsApp,
OL,9,Fand Google, which owns YouTube.
OL,11,FThey accused the companies of
OL,12,Fintentionally addicting Kaley as a
OL,13,Fchild, causing her to develop anxiety,
OL,14,Fbody dysmorphia and suicidal thoughts.
OL,16,FDuring the opening statements of the
OL,17,Ftrial, lawyer Mark Lanier said that
OL,18,F"two of the richest corporations in
OL,19,Fhistory" have "engineered addiction in
OL,20,Fchildren's brains".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774598701
OL,3,CSocial media addiction trial: What
OL,4,Cdoes the landmark US ruling mean for
OL,5,Cthe UK?
OL,7,FLawyers alleged that features built
OL,8,Finto social media platforms, including
OL,9,Finfinite scrolling, were designed to
OL,10,Fbe addictive, adding that this
OL,11,Faddiction is "profitable" for
OL,12,Fcompanies.
OL,14,FKaley said she began using YouTube at
OL,15,Fage 6 and Instagram at age 9, telling
OL,16,Fthe jury she was on social media "all
OL,17,Fday long" as a child.
OL,19,FSnap and TikTok were also originally
OL,20,Fdefendants, but both settled out of
OL,21,Fcourt before it went to trial.
OL,26,@xD@bOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
