OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774598701
OL,3,CSocial media addiction trial: What
OL,4,Cdoes the landmark US ruling mean for
OL,5,Cthe UK?
OL,7,FWhat was the verdict, and how have big
OL,8,Ftech companies responded?
OL,10,FThe Los Angeles jury determined that
OL,11,FMeta and YouTube were negligent in the
OL,12,Fdesign or operation of their
OL,13,Frespective platforms, and that the
OL,14,Fnegligence was a substantial factor in
OL,15,Fcausing harm to Kaley.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774598701
OL,3,CSocial media addiction trial: What
OL,4,Cdoes the landmark US ruling mean for
OL,5,Cthe UK?
OL,7,FThey also concluded each company knew
OL,8,Ftheir platforms could be dangerous
OL,9,Fwhen used by a minor, and agreed that
OL,10,Fthey failed to adequately warn of that
OL,11,Fdanger, further contributing to her
OL,12,Fharm.
OL,14,FA majority of jurors agreed Kaley
OL,15,Fshould be awarded $3 million in
OL,16,Fcompensatory damages, later
OL,17,Frecommending an additional $3 million
OL,18,Fin punitive damages, after deciding
OL,19,Fthe companies acted with malice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774598701
OL,3,CSocial media addiction trial: What
OL,4,Cdoes the landmark US ruling mean for
OL,5,Cthe UK?
OL,7,FThey also determined that Meta caused
OL,8,Fthe most harm to Kaley, saying Meta
OL,9,Fshouldered 70% of the responsibility
OL,10,Fwhile YouTube bore the remaining 30%.
OL,12,FBoth companies have said they disagree
OL,13,Fwith the jury's verdict and intend to
OL,14,Fappeal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
