OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774598701
OL,3,CSocial media addiction trial: What
OL,4,Cdoes the landmark US ruling mean for
OL,5,Cthe UK?
OL,7,FMeta argued that Kaley's mental health
OL,8,Fstruggles were not connected to her
OL,9,Fsocial media use and pointed to her
OL,10,Fturbulent home life, adding that "not
OL,11,Fone of her therapists identified
OL,12,Fsocial media as the cause" of her
OL,13,Fmental health issues.
OL,15,FIt's the second verdict against Meta
OL,16,Fthis week, after a jury in New Mexico
OL,17,Fdetermined the company harms
OL,18,Fchildren's mental health and safety,
OL,19,Fin violation of state law.
OL,26,@rD@bOUtD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
