CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774598701
OL,3,CSocial media addiction trial: What
OL,4,Cdoes the landmark US ruling mean for
OL,5,Cthe UK?
OL,7,FMeanwhile, YouTube focused more on the
OL,8,Fnature of the platform, arguing that
OL,9,Fit's a video platform akin to
OL,10,Ftelevision, rather than a social media
OL,11,Fplatform.
OL,13,FLawyers representing both platforms
OL,14,Falso pointed to their safety features
OL,15,Fand guardrails for users to monitor
OL,16,Fand customise their use.JHow could
OL,17,Fthis ruling have significance here in
OL,18,Fthe UK?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774598701
OL,3,CSocial media addiction trial: What
OL,4,Cdoes the landmark US ruling mean for
OL,5,Cthe UK?
OL,7,FThis verdict doesn't mandate specific
OL,8,Fchanges to the design of social media
OL,9,Fplatforms, nor to the algorithms
OL,10,Fbehind their success.
OL,12,FHowever, Prof Lorna Woods, Professor
OL,13,Fof Internet Law at the University of
OL,14,FEssex, told ITV News that the verdict
OL,15,Fof this case is "potentially very
OL,16,Fimportant", as although "damages don't
OL,17,Frequire behaviour change", it does
OL,18,F"incentivise change."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774598701
OL,3,CSocial media addiction trial: What
OL,4,Cdoes the landmark US ruling mean for
OL,5,Cthe UK?
OL,7,FShe explained: "The amount of damages
OL,8,Fawarded are dwarfed by the billion
OL,9,Fdollar revenue the companies have.
OL,11,F"Nonetheless, if the principle is
OL,12,Festablished, that opens the door for
OL,13,Fother claimants, that's the point at
OL,14,Fwhich the damages start to add up."
OL,16,FProfessor Wood added that while the
OL,17,Fcase is "not a high status case in
OL,18,Fterms of precedent setting in a formal
OL,19,Flegal sense", "nonetheless, this case
OL,20,Fis significant symbolically".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
