OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774598701
OL,3,CSocial media addiction trial: What
OL,4,Cdoes the landmark US ruling mean for
OL,5,Cthe UK?
OL,7,FThis case is the first in a number of
OL,8,Fbellwether cases, which are a small,
OL,9,Frepresentative group of cases selected
OL,10,Ffrom a larger mass of similar cases to
OL,11,Fbe tried first.
OL,13,FBellwether cases are designed to be
OL,14,Fused as a reference point for
OL,15,Flitigation, and there are several more
OL,16,Fset to take place in the first half of
OL,17,Fthis year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774598701
OL,3,CSocial media addiction trial: What
OL,4,Cdoes the landmark US ruling mean for
OL,5,Cthe UK?
OL,7,FTerry Green, Deputy Managing Partner
OL,8,Fat Katten Muchin Rosenman, explains
OL,9,Fthat "social media companies may be
OL,10,Fforced to settle outstanding claims as
OL,11,Fpart of the wider litigation and make
OL,12,Fsignificant changes to their features."
OL,14,FHe adds: "Cases like this have been
OL,15,Ftaking place in this manner due to the
OL,16,Fabsence of a clear digital platform
OL,17,Fregime in the United States."
OL,19,F"This case is unlikely to affect UK
OL,20,Fpolicy and decisions, as the UK has a
OL,21,Fclearer regime in place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774598701
OL,3,CSocial media addiction trial: What
OL,4,Cdoes the landmark US ruling mean for
OL,5,Cthe UK?
OL,7,F"Platforms already have an established
OL,8,Flegal duty of care and duty to protect
OL,9,Fchildren under the Online Safety Act."
OL,11,FWhat is the UK government doing about
OL,12,Fphone addiction, and could we see an
OL,13,Funder 16s ban?
OL,15,FThe case comes at a time where social
OL,16,Fmedia addiction is a topic in constant
OL,17,Fdiscussion.
OL,19,FSpeaking on Thursday morning, Sir Kier
OL,20,FStarmer said the government will
OL,21,F"study the ruling very carefully".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31416
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774598701
OL,3,CSocial media addiction trial: What
OL,4,Cdoes the landmark US ruling mean for
OL,5,Cthe UK?
OL,7,F"We need to do more to protect
OL,8,Fchildren", he added, speaking from
OL,9,FHelsinki where he was attending a
OL,10,Fmajor European defence summit.
OL,12,FOn Wednesday, it was announced that
OL,13,Fthe government is to trial social
OL,14,Fmedia bans and digital curfews in the
OL,15,Fhomes of 300 teenagers in the UK.
OL,17,FThis comes four months after Australia
OL,18,Fbanned under-16s from accessing social
OL,19,Fmedia apps, amid calls from some
OL,20,Fcampaigners and politicians to
OL,21,Fimplement similar measures in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31417
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774598701
OL,3,CSocial media addiction trial: What
OL,4,Cdoes the landmark US ruling mean for
OL,5,Cthe UK?
OL,7,FOther countries which have made steps
OL,8,Ftowards a ban include France, Spain
OL,9,Fand Denmark.
OL,11,FThe pilot will run alongside the
OL,12,Fdigital wellbeing consultation, which
OL,13,Fwill close on May 26 this year.
OL,15,FStarmer said on Thursday: "We are
OL,16,Fconsulting about issues such as
OL,17,Fbanning social media for under-16s."
OL,19,FHe added: "I'm very keen that we do
OL,20,Fmore on addictive features within
OL,21,Fsocial media.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31418
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774598701
OL,3,CSocial media addiction trial: What
OL,4,Cdoes the landmark US ruling mean for
OL,5,Cthe UK?
OL,7,F"We've already taken the powers, so
OL,8,Fwhen we get to the consolation we
OL,9,Fdon't have to wait years to implement
OL,10,Fthis.
OL,12,F"But I want to be really clear, it's
OL,13,Fnot if things are going to change,
OL,14,Fthings are going to change, the
OL,15,Fquestion is how much and what are we
OL,16,Fgoing to do."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
