OL,3,CSocial media addiction trial: What
OL,4,Cdoes the landmark US ruling mean for
OL,5,Cthe UK?
OL,7,FThis week, the House of Lords again
OL,8,Fsupported a proposal to ban under 16s
OL,9,Fin the UK from social media, the
OL,10,Fsecond time peers have defeated the
OL,11,Fgovernment over the proposal.
OL,13,FWhile some experts, parents and
OL,14,Fcampaigners have shown support towards
OL,15,Fthe move, others have said this could
OL,16,Fput young people in further danger by
OL,17,Fpushing them to other areas of the
OL,18,Finternet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
